      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL PLAYER (1) comes here after rocketing around this track over 400m in 22.02, claiming a NG by 1.5 lengths. Has the ability and expected to go close again. REIKO BATTY (2) has a strong record this trip with seven wins and four placings from 16 starts. Below best last time at Richmond Straight (17.98) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a 6 length sixth. Can hit the frame with the right run. MATT JET POWER (4) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at The Gardens over 400m behind You Never Lose (23.79) in a Grade 4/5. Was a winner the start prior. Has ability and can atone. LOOK FOR LIONEL (7) is new to this course but should be in the mix.",
